Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝啊 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝啊 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝啊 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝啊 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝啊 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.81,0:01:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个擦擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这上面有咱的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱可是担心死汝了
