Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:10.96,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,538)}与
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:10.96,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(633,538)}嫣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:10.96,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(705,538)}然
